cs.CR, cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.MM

The paper deals with key management in wireless sensor networks, which is a topic related to cryptography and security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the use of wireless channels for key generation, which involves information theory (cs.IT) and networking (cs.NI). The implementation of the protocol on MICAz motes involves embedded systems (cs.SY) and the evaluation of the protocol's performance involves experimental methods (cs.MM).
